snippet.title: Microsoft Flight - Overview Trailer
snippet.description:
Microsoft's famous flight simulator series returns in the latest 2012 version of "Flight." With realistic locations ranging from tropical islands to urban skylines, explore the world of this Free-to-Play PC exclusive in real world aircraft.

Fly over to IGN for more info:
http://pc.ign.com/objects/083/083711.html
